linkjvm.high.vision

Class CameraConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • linkjvm.high.vision.CameraConfig

  • public class CameraConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this object represents a camera configuration. Every camera consists out of 3 components:
    • InputProvider: The input provider provides the raw image.
    • Resolution: The resulution specifies the resolution for the processed image.
    • ChannelConfig: The channel config offers configuration for the image processing.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Version:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Markus Klein
